item.title: [+447] Feds Raid Gibson Guitars For Using Illegal Wood
item.description: US Fish & Wildlife Services agents issued a search warrant on Gibson Guitars' manufacturing plant in Nashville, TN. At issue is whether Gibson violated the Lacey Act, which prohibits the importation of rosewood from Madagascar because it serves as a home for lemurs.

item.title: [+411] Jimi Hendrix's Voodoo Child named best guitar riff
